- Real examples in this project:
  * Payment: Using Strategy Pattern to switch from Transfi to Pay2Pay
  * Trading: Using Strategy Pattern to support multiple brokers (Alpaca, Interactive Brokers, etc.)
  * Identity: Using Strategy Pattern for multiple auth methods (email/password, OAuth, passkeys)
